INSERT INTO `static_contents` VALUES ('32', 'profile', 'Sari Mas Permai\n\n33Sari Mas Permai\n  21', 'For more than 33 years, Sari Mas Permai has committed ourselves to provide our customers with high quality products and services through premium quality raw materials and strict manufacturing practices. Today we maintain our main office in Surabaya, East Java Indonesia and are exporting our products to more than 26 countries in Asia Pacific, Middle East, Africa, Europe and America. Our success comes from direct collaboration of our 300 qualified, dedicated and motivated employees with the latest manufacturing technologies and innovations. In Sari Mas Permai., we constantly strive to become your most reliable and trusted business partner, capable of delivering value added solutions to suit your needs in today\'s global marketplace. We are always receptive to the market demands and constantly searching for innovative business solutions. We believe that through our commitments, dedications and proven track records in the edible oil industries, we can provide a mutually beneficial relationship to our business partners and together, we will continue to grow well in the 21st century.', 'Selama lebih dari 33 tahun, Sari Mas Permai telah berkomitmen untuk menyediakan\n\npelanggan dengan produk-produk berkualitas tinggi dan layanan terbaik melalui bahan\n\nbaku kualitas premium dan praktek manufaktur yang ketat. Di Sari Mas Permai, kami\n\nselalu berusaha untuk menjadi mitra bisnis yang paling dapat diandalkan dan terpercaya\n\nbagi Anda, kami mampu memberikan nilai solusi tambah untuk memenuhi kebutuhan\n\nAnda di pasar global. Kami percaya bahwa melalui komitmen kami, dedikasi dan track\n\nrecord yang terbukti dalam industri minyak makan, kami dapat memberikan hubungan\n\nyang saling menguntungkan untuk mitra bisnis kami dan bersama-sama, kita akan terus\n\ntumbuh dengan baik di abad ke-21.', '33   , Sari Mas Permai       \n\n         . Sari Mas\n\nPermai ,        , \n\n  